  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They told me that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you can speak English if you speak.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And for six months, I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they told me, from now on, it's all Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You write Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You speak Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You treat in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when my father arrived, he brought my diploma out from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I was quite legitimate at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In an ulpan, which is a, a night study.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And fortunately, I met my wife, who spoke Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she taught me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yoel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zahava, Zahava Yoel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was a, a Chilean born from San-- Santiago de Chile.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's very trivial-- in the swimming pool.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We met in the swimming pool, and when she had a day off and, and I had also day off.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then an older gentleman who was with me, he introduced us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that, that somehow, my, my whole life has been paved with fortunate accidents, sometimes not so the misfortunate, that the fact that my mother died, that's why I went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if I had not gone to Israel, I would have never met her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And that was a great experience, to be in Israel for five years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it really had nothing to do with life or economics that I came here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I always wanted to come to the United States after that experience of liberation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And my mother also always pumped it in me, you should go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When you grow up, you should go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the-- well, she had personal connections.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her, her father lived here in Brooklyn, my grandpa, and her sisters and brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
